# Diese Grundbausteine müssen in allen Libaries eingehalten werden !!!


Example Libarie `lib/test.cpp`:
``` cpp
#include "test.h"
TestC Test;

void TestC::init(){
  Serial.println("Hello World");
}

```

Example Libarie `lib/test.h`:
``` h
#pragma once
#include "Elementar.h"

class TestC{
    private:
    public:
        void init();
};

extern TestC Test;

```